# Business Model — Affordable Construction Marketplace
# Author: Andres Gamboa
# Date: February 2026

This document outlines the revenue model and financial structure of the Affordable Construction Marketplace.

---

## Core Revenue Model

### 1. Commission Per Deal
The platform is free to use. Revenue is generated through a small commission taken from each completed job agreement.

### Commission Structure (Draft)
- 5%–12% commission per completed job
- Commission percentage may vary based on:
  - Job size
  - Contractor tier
  - Customer membership level

### Example:
- Customer and contractor agree on $500
- Platform takes 8% ($40)
- Contractor receives $460

---

## Why Commission-Based?
- Keeps the platform free for browsing
- Encourages more users to join
- Only charges when real value is delivered
- Scales with platform usage

---

